It is important for us to contribute the patches and improvements we made to various software back to the original project. So everyone can benefit from the improvements and we don't need to maintain and carry around patches.

=== Successful ===

* <code>2017-08-14</code> libSDL: [https://bugzilla.libsdl.org/show_bug.cgi?id=3751 DirectFB linux_input disabled by default]
* <code>2017-08-03</code> Alpine Linux: [https://github.com/alpinelinux/aports/pull/2057 add consolekit2]
* <code>2017-07-21</code> abuild: [https://github.com/alpinelinux/abuild/pull/21 <code>-D</code> parameter for alternative description]
* <code>2017-07-07</code> Alpine Linux: [https://github.com/alpinelinux/aports/pull/1092 busybox-extras with telnetd enabled]
* <code>2017-05-23</code> weston: [https://patchwork.freedesktop.org/patch/150943/ instead of less than 1 Hz use default refresh rate]

